{
  "doc_id": "45680",
  "text": "Measures in the X:IT study are mainly based on measures used in international validated studies, ESFA [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , and HBSC [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . Measures developed for the X:IT study have been tested for face validity in the pilot tests, but are not validated any further.",
